{"title":"未成年人ICP备案注意事项","uid":"42eac52e5e3ab091dbedcb3a931ab7e9","slug":"未成年人ICP备案注意事项","date":"2023-07-20T15:26:21.000Z","updated":"2023-07-20T15:38:21.789Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/未成年人ICP备案注意事项.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"未成年人ICP备案注意事项\"><a href=\"#未成年人ICP备案注意事项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"未成年人ICP备案注意事项\"></a>未成年人ICP备案注意事项</h1><hr>\n<h3 id=\"查阅当地信通院备案年龄要求\"><a href=\"#查阅当地信通院备案年龄要求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查阅当地信通院备案年龄要求\"></a>查阅当地信通院备案年龄要求</h3><p>可以前往<a href=\"https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/116031.html?spm=a2c4g.50264.0.0.4f945519wWGAVM\">阿里云</a>查看各地管局对ICP备案的年龄要求</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>注：各地区管局要求可能会有所差异</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"准备所需材料\"><a href=\"#准备所需材料\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"准备所需材料\"></a>准备所需材料</h3><h5 id=\"个人材料：\"><a href=\"#个人材料：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"个人材料：\"></a>个人材料：</h5><p>1.个人身份证件（身份证，护照等）</p>\n<p>2.承诺书，内容:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>介绍网站内容 </p>\n</li>\n<li><p>与监护人是什么关系</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>承诺所有网站都是本人使用，不做违法违规信息，否则愿意接受注销网站并列入域名黑名单的处罚。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>3.朗读视频，朗读内容：我叫xxx（备案人），此次备案主体为xxx（备案主体），我愿意为提交的备案信息真实性负责，时间：YYYY年MM月DD日</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>视频中时间不要与提交备案时间超过三天</p></blockquote>\n<p>其他辅助材料：</p>\n<p>1.父母任意一方身份证（用于证明监护关系）</p>\n<h3 id=\"备案步骤\"><a href=\"#备案步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"备案步骤\"></a>备案步骤</h3><ol>\n<li>前往阿里云主页点击ICP备案</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://source.tuftech.org/beian1.png\" alt=\"备案\"></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>选择开始备案</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://source.tuftech.org/beian2.png\" alt=\"备案\"></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>选择免费，开始备案</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://source.tuftech.org/beian3.png\" alt=\"备案\"></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>选择要备案的域名</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>由于我已经完成备案所以可能会有些出入</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://source.tuftech.org/beian4.png\" alt=\"备案\"></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>根据提示一步一步提交材料进行备案</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"注意事项\"><a href=\"#注意事项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意事项\"></a>注意事项</h3><ul>\n<li>提交的材料要保证真实性和及时性，避免相差时间太久</li>\n<li>注意接听阿里云客服的电话：95187，(0571) 2895 0440</li>\n<li>再收到短信核验后，必须在24小时内进入<a href=\"http://beian.miit.gov.cn/\">工信部网站</a>完成短信核验</li>\n</ul>\n<p>最后祝各位备案成功</p>\n","text":"未成年人ICP备案注意事项 查阅当地信通院备案年龄要求可以前往阿里云查看各地管局对ICP备案的年龄要求 注：各地区管局要求可能会有所差异 准备所需材料个人材料：1.个人身份证件（身份证，护照等） 2.承诺书，内容: 介绍网站内容 与监护人是什么关系 承诺所有网站都是本人使用，不做...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":527,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"技术","slug":"技术","count":1,"path":"api/tags/技术.json"},{"name":"分享","slug":"分享","count":1,"path":"api/tags/分享.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BAICP%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">未成年人ICP备案注意事项</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E9%98%85%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E4%BF%A1%E9%8